      <title>祖马之女将面临与南非骚乱有关的指控</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/zuma-s-daughter-to-face-charges-related-to-south-african-riots</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前南非总统雅各布·祖马的女儿将面临与四年前该国反政府骚乱有关的指控，那场骚乱造成 354 人死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/zuma-s-daughter-to-face-charges-related-to-south-african-riots</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 07:50:55 GMT</pubDate>
